//-----------------Blade Layouts (Reusable Page Structure)////////
to avoid repeating main structure in each page see app.blade.php in the view/layouts

| Blade      | Purpose                                   |
| ---------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| `@extends` | inherit layout                            |
| `@section` | define content                            |
| `@yield`   | place content in layout                   |
| '@include' | insert a Blade file into anotherBlade file|

example for @include => @include('partials.nav')

---PASSING DATA TO @include---
@include('partials.nav', ['name' => 'Boshra'])

---Difference Between @yield and @include---

| Feature    | Purpose                     |
| ---------- | --------------------------- |
| `@yield`   | placeholder for child views |
| `@include` | insert reusable Blade files |



